headline: Why Paramount (PSKY) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of multinational media and entertainment corporation Paramount (NASDAQ:PARA) jumped 3.1% in the afternoon session after the company announced a major film deal with Microsoft-owned Activision to bring the popular “Call of Duty” video game franchise to the big screen.
